metadata.name: Natural Beauty #01
metadata.description:
This photograph comes from the "Natural Beauty" series that I began in 2020. Through the lens, I captured the female body in its natural and most elegant form. Playing with its curves and teasing out its mystique, I gave it an artistic touch by having it on black and white and creating an intense portrait that sublimates the female body.
 
Artist: Rhea Prokop
Model: Vivienne

Image size: 4074 x 6111 Pixels
Image type: JPG
